<div class="prose dark:prose-invert mb-4 sm:mb-8 mx-auto max-w-2xl">
  <h1 class="text-center"><span class="text-4xl tracking-tight">The most effortless way to publish your writing online</span></h1>
  <p class="mt-8 sm:mt-12">
    Create your own beautifully minimalist blog in seconds. Free and open source!
  </p>
  <p>
    Publish your writing effortlessly by sending an email, or use our delightfully simple editor.
  </p>
  <p>
    Check out the <a href="https://pagecord.com/pagecord">Pagecord blog</a> to see it in action.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 text-center not-prose">
    <%= link_to new_signup_path do %>
      <div class="mt-2 inline-flex font-semibold p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-white bg-bmc-pink">Start writing with Pagecord today!</div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 py-4">
  <figure>
    <%= image_tag "home/screenshot-02.webp", alt: "Pagecord screenshot", class: "dark:hidden" %>
    <%= image_tag "home/screenshot-02-dark.webp", alt: "Pagecord screenshot", class: "hidden dark:block" %>
    <figcaption class="text-center text-slate-500 text-sm px-8">
      A beautiful, minimalist blog that looks great on any device. Light or dark mode.
    </figcaption>
  </figure>

  <figure class="mt-4 sm:mt-0">
    <%= image_tag "home/screenshot-03.webp", alt: "Pagecord screenshot", class: "dark:hidden" %>
    <%= image_tag "home/screenshot-03-dark.webp", alt: "Pagecord screenshot", class: "hidden dark:block" %>
    <figcaption class="text-center text-slate-500 text-sm px-8">
      Publish new posts by sending an email, or use our delightfully simple editor
    </figcaption>
  </figure>
</div>

<div class="mt-12 prose dark:prose-invert mb-4 sm:mb-8 mx-auto max-w-2xl">
  <h2 class="text-center">Fun features. Unbeatable Value 😇</h2>
  <p>
    Pagecord is super-simple to use, but it's chock-a-block with great features.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Long-form writing or microblog</strong>. Write long-form articles or microblog your thoughts. Both look fantastic 🎨</li>
    <li><strong>Bold, underline, lists or code</strong>. Rich text formatting is fully supported 🖋️</li>
    <li><strong>Media Embeds</strong>. Links to YouTube, Spotify and Bandcamp are automatically embedded. Great for sharing your favourite tunes and videos 🎧 📺</li>
    <li><strong>Follow your friends</strong>. Pagecord is social! Follow other Pagecord blogs and see the latest articles in your personal feed 🤝</li>
    <li><strong>RSS feeds</strong>. Every site has a public RSS feed. You get a private RSS feed of all your followee's posts too! 📑</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mt-8">
    Premium customers get additional features and a warm fuzzy feeling for an unbeatable price of only <span class="px-1 font-bold bg-[#fcc7c7] dark:bg-[#ff5f5f] dark:text-white rounded">$<%= Subscription.price %> per year!</span>
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Image Attachments</strong>. Attach images to your email and they'll auto-magically appear in your posts 🪄</li>
    <li><strong>Custom Domains</strong>. If you'd prefer to use you own domain name for your site, set it up in one click 🌐</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-center">Open source 🤓</h2>
  <p>
    The Pagecord code is <a href="https://github.com/lylo/pagecord">open source under the MIT license</a>. Take a look under the hood,
    suggest improvements, or (if you're feeling brave) host it yourself!
  </p>

  <div class="mt-8 text-center not-prose">
    <%= link_to new_signup_path do %>
      <div class="mt-2 inline-flex font-semibold p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-white bg-bmc-pink">Start writing with Pagecord today!</div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <hr>

  <h3 class="text-center tracking-tight">Subscribe to the newsletter for updates</h3>
  <%= render "newsletter_form" %>
</div>
